						</svg>
						<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-white scale-[97%] rounded-full -z-10"></div>
					</A>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="max-w-132 md:ml-12 lg:ml-20 xl:ml-40">
				<p class="mt-1 text-lg lg:text-xl">
					is a <strong class="text-pink-600">designer</strong>, <strong class="text-amber-600">developer</strong>, and <strong class="text-sky-600">educator</strong>
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg lg:text-xl">
					a <strong>PhD researcher</strong> at the <A href="https://www.responsiblenlp.org/students/rayo-verweij/" class="underline-offset-2">University of Edinburgh</A>
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg lg:text-xl">
					and a <strong>mentor</strong> at and trustee of <A href="https://prewired.org" class="underline-offset-2">Prewired</A>
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg lg:text-xl">
					working on <span class="font-emoji">🧒</span> young people's critical understanding of new technologies like <span class="font-emoji">⚙️</span> AI through designing and <span class="font-emoji">🛠️</span> <strong>building their own tools</strong>
				</p>
				<p class="mt-8 flex gap-2">
					<span class="text-lg font-emoji">📧</span> rayo [dot] verweij [at] ed [dot] ac [dot] uk
				</p>

				<div class="relative mt-24 md:mt-32 lg:mt-48 md:ml-4 lg:ml-0">
